544
00:34:13,945 --> 00:34:15,383
I had sex for money.

545
00:34:19,423 --> 00:34:20,697
I was a prostitute.

546
00:34:57,830 --> 00:34:59,578
Dream or reality?

547
00:35:00,242 --> 00:35:04,732
