into the pool, didn't I?

557
00:35:33,664 --> 00:35:35,966
- You did.
- Oh, well, that's bad.

558
00:35:36,134 --> 00:35:39,428
Normally I find a brawl between
two red-blooded boys kinda hot,

559
00:35:39,596 --> 00:35:41,847
but when it's over your ex-fiancée,

560
00:35:42,588 --> 00:35:43,626
