577
00:37:00,176 --> 00:37:01,705
Thanks. That means a lot.

578
00:37:06,087 --> 00:37:08,642
About the way you took
things slow with me,

579
00:37:09,333 --> 00:37:12,173
the late shifts, mysterious texts,

580
00:37:13,712 --> 00:37:14,878
that guy Rick.

581
00:37:18,132 --> 00:37:20,153
How many times did you
look me in the eye and lie?

582
00:37:23,389 --> 00:37:24,991
And the scary thing...

583
00:37:26,448 --> 00:37:27,786
