595
00:38:29,458 --> 00:38:30,708
You're my best friend.

596
00:38:30,833 --> 00:38:32,772
I'll always be here.
Call me back, okay?

597
00:38:56,005 --> 00:38:59,176
Boy, I don't know who the jerk was
